# General pages
You can also create other pages for themes/issues of interest to the whole community in the same way indicated for Language pages. However, it is preferable to let the [Language coordinators](https://class.coursera.org/translations-001/wiki/language-coordinators) do that together.
* .....

# Existing useful resources
Several resources about translating, coordinating translations, terminology coherence, have already been posted in the GTC forums. Again, it is preferable to let the [Language coordinators](https://class.coursera.org/translations-001/wiki/language-coordinators) do that together.
* .....

